summary:
This is a modders resource aimed at recreating most of TES4 Oblivion Unique Rocks.
Currently there are 7 remade rocks available.
descriptionHtml:
[b][center][size=5][color=#ff0000]Elder Scrolls IV Oblivion[/color] Remade Small [color=#999999]Rocks[/color]
[size=1]-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[color=#0000ff][size=3][/size][/color][url=https://www.facebook.com/DaggerfallTeam/][color=#0000ff][size=3]Official Facebook Page, Like and Enjoy[/size][/color][/url]
[size=4][color=#B45F06]Details[/color]
-----------
[size=3]A small Resource that remakes the small set of Rocks that were featured in TES4 Oblivion, Currently there are 7 available and more being remade!
[/size]
[color=#38761D]Instructions[/color]
----------------
[size=3]There are No Textures for the Models, Use Nifscope to add one
There is no .esp, Use the Creation Kit to add them[/size]

[color=#BF9000]Credits[/color]
----------
[size=3]Feel Free to Use this Resource, All I ask is Credit & Comment[/size][/size][/size][/size][/center][/b]
author: DaggerfallTeam
